  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the efficacy, safety, and tolerability of treatment with sofosbuvir
      (SOF)/velpatasvir (VEL; GS-5816) fixed-dose combination (FDC) for 12 weeks in treatment-naive
      and treatment-experienced participants with chronic hepatitis C virus (HCV) infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
